# Bitscale Project Standards

## Stack

- Next.js 16 (App Router) + React 19 + TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS v4 (CSS-first config, no `tailwind.config.js`)
- Design tokens in `app/theme.css`

## Imports

- Use `@/` path alias (`@/components/...`, `@/app/...`)
- Import components directly from their file — no barrel `index.ts` re-exports

```tsx
import DashboardLayout from "@/components/templates/dashboard-layout/DashboardLayout";
```

## Code changes

- Minimize scope — only change what the task requires
- Match existing naming, types, and file structure
- Do not add docs or helpers unless asked
- Add tests when modifying critical functionality (see `testing.mdc`)

## File layout

```
app/           → routes, layouts, global styles, theme
components/    → atomic design UI (atoms → templates)
```
